description:
The 142nd 2022 US Open is the upcoming fourth and final Grand Slam event of the year. It will be held on outdoor hard courts at the USTA Billie Jean King National Tennis Center in New York City, from August 29 to September 11 2022.

This is a market on who will advance after the Men’s Singles match between Nick Kyrgios and Karen Khachanov, scheduled for September 6, 8:15 PM ET.

If Nick Kyrgios advances this market will resolve to “Kyrgios”. If Karen Khachanov advances this market will resolve to "Khachanov". Note, the market will resolve to whichever player advances, even if the result is a "walkover".

If for any reason the person advancing is not declared by organizers by September 13, 11:59:59 PM ET, the market will resolve 50-50.
